<text>Cressona is a genus of shield bugs in the subfamily Phyllocephalinae, erected by William Sweetland Dallas in 1851.

==Species==
The following are included in &quot;BioLib.cz&quot;:
# &quot;Cressona divaricata&quot; 
# &quot;Cressona rufa&quot; 
# &quot;Cressona valida&quot; - type species, Myanmar

