** Transport Squadron 841 (operating Boeing B-737-200, Boeing 737-500)
** Transport Squadron 842 (operating L-100-20 Hercules)
** Transport Squadron 843 (operating An-32B)
** Transport Squadron 844 (operating C-27J Spartan)
